  "description": "# Spokane, WA · GEG\n\nThe Lilac City; largest metro in the Inland Northwest. Coverage centers on Spokane and its immediate suburbs along the Spokane River corridor.\n\n## Coverage\n\n<table style=\"width: auto\">\n<tr><td><strong>Region</strong></td><td>Spokane metro, Washington (US)</td></tr>\n<tr><td><strong>Bounding Box</strong></td><td>-117.608, 47.570 → -117.109, 47.797</td></tr>\n<tr><td><strong>Playable Area</strong></td><td>~950 km²</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n## Population Summary\n\n<table style=\"width: auto\">\n<tr><td><strong>Metro Population</strong></td><td align=\"right\">560,000</td></tr>\n<tr><td><strong>Total Modeled Demand</strong></td><td align=\"right\">157,109</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n## Map Statistics\n\n<table style=\"width: auto\">\n<tr><td><strong>Buildings Indexed</strong></td><td align=\"right\">130,763</td></tr>\n<tr><td><strong>Demand Points</strong></td><td align=\"right\">519</td></tr>\n<tr><td><strong>Population Nodes</strong></td><td align=\"right\">16,695</td></tr>\n<tr><td><strong>Median Commute Distance</strong></td><td align=\"right\">12.5 km</td></tr>\n<tr><td><strong>Mean Commute Distance</strong></td><td align=\"right\">13.6 km</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n## Additional Features\n\n- **Building Collision** — A buildings index of 130,763 structures is included, providing in-game collision geometry for all non-filtered buildings.\n- **Road & Runway Overlays** — Road network plus runway/taxiway geometry are bundled, covering Spokane International Airport (GEG) and surface routing across the metro.",
